                        "Tailwind CSS utility classes for Sky.Live apps. Type-safe, composable, zero-runtime — class names checked at compile time."
                        "github.com/anzellai/sky-tailwind ->"
                        "https://github.com/anzellai/sky-tailwind"
                  , projectCard
                        "SkyVote"
